reviewText: The greatest gun series of all time!!! If you're a fan of firearms or want to learn more about them, this series is an excellent and entertaining way to go about that... It isn't a reality show, like "Sons of Guns" or "American Guns", but rather an actual educational program, about the history of firearms.
